## 2026-04-05 - Publish readiness checks require manual re-triggering after fixing issues
- Fixed a TDZ bug in `PublishPanel.tsx` where `runReadinessChecks` was referenced before its `useCallback` declaration (line 259 used `runReadinessChecks` defined at line 342 вҖ” crashing on first render). Fixed by moving the `runReadinessChecks` useCallback and its `READINESS_TIMEOUT_MS` constant to BEFORE the auto-run effects section.
