- The command palette "Recently Edited" section and token list "recently touched" filter already existed but were backed by `useRecentlyTouched` which was in-memory only (reset on every plugin reload). `recentTokens.ts` had `addRecentToken`/`getRecentTokens` localStorage helpers that were defined but never called.
