## 2026-04-05 - Publish readiness checks don't auto-rerun after fixing issues
- Added two new auto-rerun triggers in `useReadinessChecks.ts`:
  1. `useEffect` watching `checksStale` + `connected` + `activeSet`: when a sync/apply operation marks checks stale (varSync.applyDiff, styleSync.applyDiff, git.applyDiff), checks now auto-rerun instead of requiring a manual "Re-check" click
  2. `useEffect` with a `window` `message` listener for `variables-applied`: when Figma confirms the "Push missing variables" fix completed, checks auto-rerun to reflect the new state

