## 2026-04-05 - ThemeManager coverage visualization shows only gap counts, not a visual matrix
- Created `ThemeCoverageMatrix.tsx` (new component, ~270 lines): per-dimension matrix showing token groups Г— theme options with fill status. Each cell shows вң“ (complete), an orange count (unresolved aliases), a violet count (missing overrides), or "вҖ“" (option has no tokens in that group). Clicking any cell navigates back to the list view with that dimension+option selected.
